    • Constructor Detail

      • Command

        public Command(java.lang.String func,
       Stackable attr,
       java.lang.String lbl)
        Default constructor.
        Stores a triple with assembly function, attribute stackable and label. If one of them does not exist, a null reference must be passed.

        Once created, the command cannot be changed.

        Parameters:
        func - String with an assembly function (or null, if none avaiable)
        attr - String with the function's attribute (or null, if none avaiable or required)
        lbl - String with a specified label (or null, if none avaiable)
